description: Returns the count of compliant and noncompliant conformance packs across all Amazon Web Services accounts and Amazon Web Services Regions in an aggregator. You can filter based on Amazon Web Services account ID or Amazon Web Services Region.

parameters.name: ConfigurationAggregatorName
parameters.description: The name of the configuration aggregator.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: Filters the results based on the AggregateConformancePackComplianceSummaryFilters object. AccountId (string) --- The 12-digit Amazon Web Services account ID of the source account. AwsRegion (string) --- The source Amazon Web Services Region from where the data is aggregated.

nested_params.name: AccountId
nested_params.description: The 12-digit Amazon Web Services account ID of the source account.

nested_params.name: AwsRegion
nested_params.description: The source Amazon Web Services Region from where the data is aggregated.

nested_items.name: AggregateConformancePackComplianceSummaries
nested_items.description: Returns a list of AggregateConformancePackComplianceSummary object.

nested_items.name: GroupName
nested_items.description: Groups the result based on Amazon Web Services account ID or Amazon Web Services Region.

nested_items.name: GroupByKey
nested_items.description: Groups the result based on Amazon Web Services account ID or Amazon Web Services Region.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The nextToken string returned on a previous page that you use to get the next page of results in a paginated response.
